== About Me
I am a third-year undergraduate student majoring in data science at [https://cuhk.edu.cn/en/ The Chinese University of Hong Kong, Shenzhen (CUHK-Shenzhen)].
I am also affiliated with the [https://sse.cuhk.edu.cn/en/ School of Science and Engineering] of CUHK-Shenzhen as a research assistant. 
My main research interests include:
- Federated learning
- Gaussian processes
- Signal processing

Currently, I am working with [https://sse.cuhk.edu.cn/en/teacher/355 Zhidi Lin] and [https://sse.cuhk.edu.cn/en/faculty/yinfeng Prof. Feng Yin] on spectral kernel 
design for Gaussian processes.
	
== Recent News
- /June, 2021/: The paper \"Demystifying Model Averaging for Communication-Efficient Federated Matrix Factorization\" is accepted 
at *[https://www.2021.ieeeicassp.org/ IEEE International Conference on Acoustics, Speech and Signal Processing (ICASSP) 2021]*. 
Check out the paper on [https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/9413927 IEEE Xplore].

