- /January, 2021/: Delivered a workshop at *PPSD Surabaya Coding Workshop Series* on /Data Analysis with Pandas/. 
Watch the recording [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nPe2FzJP3n8&feature=youtu.be here].
- /November, 2020/: Received the *2020 Guangdong Provincial Government Outstanding International Student Scholarship*. 
This scholarship is awarded to outstanding international students in colleges and universities across the Guangdong province.
- /June, 2020/: Awarded the third prize at *Computer Engineering (CE) Camp 2020* held by the School of Science and Engineering of CUHK-Shenzhen (with Yupeng Yang). 
Our project topic was federated unsupervised learning (with applications to clustering, topic modeling, and recommendation systems) and 
we were fortunate to be supervised by [https://myweb.cuhk.edu.cn/changtsunghui/Home/Index Prof. Tsung-Hui Chang].
